<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cara Pesan - TravelTrain</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@600;700;800&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: { sans: ['Poppins', 'sans-serif'], heading: ['Montserrat', 'sans-serif'] },
                    colors: { primary: '#4F46E5', secondary: '#EC4899' }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-gray-700">

    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 top-0 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 group">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary to-secondary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-gray-800">Kembali</span>
            </a>
            <span class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-primary">Panduan Pemesanan</span>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-28 pb-20">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Cara Mudah Pesan Tiket</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-500">Ikuti 3 langkah sederhana ini untuk memulai perjalananmu.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-indigo-50 hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary text-2xl font-bold mb-6">1</div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">Cari Jadwal</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pilih stasiun asal, tujuan, dan tanggal keberangkatan di halaman utama. Klik "Cari Tiket".</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-pink-50 hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-pink-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-secondary text-2xl font-bold mb-6">2</div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">Isi Data Diri</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pilih kereta yang diinginkan, lalu isi data penumpang (Nama & NIK) dengan benar.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-purple-50 hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-purple-600 text-2xl font-bold mb-6">3</div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">Bayar & Berangkat</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Lakukan pembayaran via Transfer/QRIS. E-Ticket akan muncul di menu "Tiket Saya".</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 text-center">
            <a href="/" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white font-bold py-3 px-10 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-indigo-500/50 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                Pesan Sekarang
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>